    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">私</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">わたし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">家</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>にきた<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">盲目</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">めくら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">帰</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かえ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>りにあんずの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">花</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">折</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">お</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>って、<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">夏</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">なつ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>がきたら、またこよう。<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">赤</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あか</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>いお<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">月</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">つき</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>さま<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">出</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">で</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>る<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">晩</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ばん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に。<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">俺</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おれ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>はくるくる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">青坊主</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あおぼうず</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">笠</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かさ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>をかぶって<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">坊</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ぼっ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ちゃんの、<lb />
お<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">家</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">いえ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">窓</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">まど</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>から、のぞきましょう。<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
